item.title: First Go Project
item.description: Fighting(PVP) and taking contol of systems is one of the core elements in Eve online, each player has a spaceship with modules at their disposal to use in those fights. Getting those items can take quite a while, each player has to haul their ship with modules from a trade-hub(Jita) to their favorite system. The market in Eve online is another core element that can be a lucrative business. Why not take advantage of that?
